{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"46d6b7215c","title":"搞社会主义我们还没有一套，还要碰钉子","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9df227b123","index":0,"year":1961,"month":8,"day":23,"articleId":"46d6b7215c"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji44","name":"毛泽东全集第44卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/44-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji44":{"comments":[{"id":"b37e923a8b","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"46d6b7215c","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"胡乔木，当时任中共中央书记处候补书记、毛泽东的秘书。"},{"id":"c259dffecd","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"46d6b7215c","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"参见曹操《步出夏门行》。中华书局1959年出版的《曹操集》中作：“盈缩之期，不但在天。养怡之福，可得永年。"},{"id":"03d0051072","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"46d6b7215c","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈云，当时任中共中央副主席、国务院副总理。林彪，当时任中共中央副主席、中央军委副主席、国务院副总理。康生，当时任中共中央政治局候补委员。"},{"id":"0aeef400a1","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"46d6b7215c","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"谷羽，胡乔木的夫人"}],"contents":[{"id":"bee0400688","type":"title","text":"给胡乔木的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"46d6b7215c"},{"id":"b37e923a8b","type":"paragraph","text":"乔木同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"46d6b7215c"},{"id":"c259dffecd","type":"paragraph","text":"八月十七日信收到，甚念。你须长期休养，不计时日，以愈为度。曹操诗云：盈缩之期，不独在天。养怡之福，可以永年。回此诗宜读。你似以迁地疗养为宜，随气候转移，从事游山玩水，专看闲书，不看正书，也不管时事，如此可能好得快些。作一、二、三年休养打算，不要只作几个月打算。如果急于工作，恐又将复发。你的病近似陈云、林彪、康生诸同志，林、康因长期休养，病已好了，陈病亦有进步，可以效法。问谷羽好。如你转地疗养，谷宜随去。以上建议，请你们二人商量的定。我身心尚好，顺告，勿念。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"46d6b7215c"},{"id":"03d0051072","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"46d6b7215c"},{"id":"0aeef400a1","type":"paragraph","text":"1961年八月二十五日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"46d6b7215c"}],"page":{"id":"e7612e3568","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"46d6b7215c","start":348,"end":348}}}},"__N_SSG":true}